      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הוּא כְּרַגְלֵי אוֹתָהּ הָעִיר<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"221\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"195\" data-sentence-id=\"5\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"א\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>הַשּׁוֹאֵל כְּלִי",
