    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵחֲבֵירוֹ מֵעֶרֶב יוֹם<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"222\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> טוֹב. פְּשִׁיטָא! לָא צְרִיכָא,",
