    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לוֹ אֶלָּא בְּיוֹם טוֹב — הֲרֵי הוּא כְּרַגְלֵי הַשּׁוֹאֵל<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"223\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"196\" data-sentence-id=\"7\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ב\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>בְּיוֹם טוֹב —",
