      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כְּרַגְלֵי הַמַּשְׁאִיל<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"224\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> פְּשִׁיטָא! לָא צְרִיכָא,",
