      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַשְׁכַּח אִינִישׁ אַחֲרִינָא וְאָזֵיל וְשָׁאֵיל מִינֵּיהּ<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"225\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"197\" data-sentence-id=\"8\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ג\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְכֵן",
