        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הָאִשָּׁה שֶׁשָּׁאֲלָה מֵחֲבֶרְתָּהּ<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"226\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> כִּי סְלֵיק <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Akiva I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"6\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Akiva I\" data-name-he=\"רבי אבא\">רַבִּי אַבָּא</span>",
