      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָמַר: יְהֵא רַעֲוָא דְּאֵימָא מִלְּתָא דְּתִתְקַבַּל. כִּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "סְלֵיק, אַשְׁכְּחֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yoḥanan II, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1570\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yoḥanan II\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוחנן\">לְרַבִּי יוֹחָנָן</span> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-unknown\" data-sage-type=\"unknown\" title=\"Rabbi Ḥanina bar Pappi\" data-authority-id=\"22004\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Ḥanina bar Pappi\" data-name-he=\"רבי חנינא בר פפי\">וְרַבִּי חֲנִינָא בַּר פַּפִּי</span>",
